{
  "name": "Kayaking",
  "overview": "Kayaking has become one of the fastest-growing paddlesports in the United States. An estimated nine million Americans enjoy this sport. The most popular style of kayaking is recreational kayaking, followed by touring/sea kayaking, and whitewater kayaking. This merit badge will introduce you to recreational kayaking and help prepare you for advanced paddlesports such as tour/sea and whitewater kayaking.",
  "is_eagle_required": false,
  "is_lab": false,
  "url": "https://www.scouting.org/merit-badges/kayaking/",
  "pdf_url": "https://filestore.scouting.org/filestore/Merit_Badge_ReqandRes/Pamphlets/Kayaking.pdf",
  "workbook_pdf_url": "http://usscouts.org/mb/worksheets/Kayaking.pdf",
  "workbook_docx_url": "http://usscouts.org/mb/worksheets/Kayaking.docx",
  "shop_url": "https://www.scoutshop.org/kayaking-merit-badge-pamphlet-650732.html",
  "image_url": "https://www.scouting.org/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Kayaking-qjjk7o9kq7qcbw6yfhc6pk66ya5ahli8rqabu8xaw0.png",
  "image_filename": "kayaking-merit-badge.jpg",
  "requirements": [
    {
      "id": "8978",
      "label": "1",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Do the following:"
        }
      ],
      "resources": [],
      "sub_requirements": [
        {
          "id": "8979",
          "label": "a",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Explain to your counselor the hazards you are most likely to encounter while participating in kayaking activities, including weather and water-related hazards, and what you should do to anticipate, help prevent, mitigate, and respond to these hazards."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8980",
          "label": "b",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Review prevention, symptoms, and first-aid treatment for the following injuries or illnesses that can occur while kayaking: blisters, cold-water shock and hypothermia, heat-related illnesses, dehydration, sunburn, sprains, and strains."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8981",
          "label": "c",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Review the Scouting America Safety Afloat policy. Explain to your counselor how this applies to kayaking."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "8982",
      "label": "2",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Before doing requirements 3 through 8, successfully complete the Scouting America swimmer test. "
        },
        {
          "type": "element",
          "tag": "br",
          "attrs": {},
          "children": []
        },
        {
          "type": "element",
          "tag": "b",
          "attrs": {},
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Note:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": " See the "
        },
        {
          "type": "element",
          "tag": "i",
          "attrs": {},
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Swimming"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": " merit badge pamphlet for details about the Scouting America swimmer test."
        }
      ],
      "resources": [],
      "sub_requirements": []
    },
    {
      "id": "8948",
      "label": "3",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Do the following:"
        }
      ],
      "resources": [],
      "sub_requirements": [
        {
          "id": "8949",
          "label": "a",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Review the characteristics of life jackets most appropriate for kayaking and understand why one must always be worn while paddling. Then demonstrate how to select and fit a life jacket for kayaking."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8950",
          "label": "b",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Review the importance of safety equipment such as a signal device, extra paddle, sponge, bilge pump, flotation bags, and throw bag."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "8951",
      "label": "4",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Do the following:"
        }
      ],
      "resources": [],
      "sub_requirements": [
        {
          "id": "8952",
          "label": "a",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Name and point out the major parts of a kayak."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8953",
          "label": "b",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Review the differences in the design between recreational, whitewater, and sea or touring kayaks. Include how length, width, stability, and rocker are involved in the design of each type."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8954",
          "label": "c",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Explain the care, maintenance, and storage of a kayak."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "8956",
      "label": "5",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Discuss the following:"
        }
      ],
      "resources": [],
      "sub_requirements": [
        {
          "id": "8957",
          "label": "a",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Correct methods for the use of a kayak paddle."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8983",
          "label": "b",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Parts of a paddle."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8958",
          "label": "c",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The care and maintenance of a paddle."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "8959",
      "label": "6",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Using a properly equipped kayak with an open cockpit, a sit-on-top, or an inflatable kayak, do the following:"
        }
      ],
      "resources": [],
      "sub_requirements": [
        {
          "id": "8960",
          "label": "a",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Safely capsize and perform a wet exit."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8961",
          "label": "b",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Reenter the kayak with assistance from a buddy boat."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8962",
          "label": "c",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Demonstrate a kayak-over-kayak rescue."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8963",
          "label": "d",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Demonstrate the HELP position."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8964",
          "label": "e",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Capsize the kayak, swim it and the paddle to shore, and empty water from the kayak with assistance if needed."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "8965",
      "label": "7",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "As a solo paddler, use a properly equipped kayak to demonstrate the following:"
        }
      ],
      "resources": [],
      "sub_requirements": [
        {
          "id": "8966",
          "label": "a",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Forward stroke"
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8967",
          "label": "b",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Backstroke"
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8968",
          "label": "c",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Forward sweep"
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8969",
          "label": "d",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Reverse sweep"
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8970",
          "label": "e",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Draw stroke"
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8971",
          "label": "f",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Stern draw."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "8972",
      "label": "8",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "As a solo paddler, use a properly equipped kayak to demonstrate the following:"
        }
      ],
      "resources": [],
      "sub_requirements": [
        {
          "id": "8973",
          "label": "a",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Paddle a straight line for 15 to 20 boat lengths using appropriate strokes while maintaining trim and balance of the kayak."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8974",
          "label": "b",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Spin or pivot from a stationary position 180 degrees (half circle) to the right and left within two boat lengths."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8975",
          "label": "c",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Move abeam to the right 10 feet and to the left 10 feet."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8976",
          "label": "d",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Stop the boat in one boat length."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8977",
          "label": "e",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "While maintaining forward motion, turn the kayak 90 degrees to the right and left."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8984",
          "label": "f",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Move the kayak backward three to four boat lengths using appropriate and effective reverse strokes."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "8985",
          "label": "g",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Paddle the kayak in a buoyed figure 8 course around markers three to four boat lengths apart."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}